OL,5, It is too expensive for governments to 
OL,6, help everyone with their soaring energy
OL,7, bills, the World Bank has warned.      
OL,9,FThe bank's president said Covid support
OL,10,Fschemes had not been targeted enough   
OL,11,Ftowards the most vulnerable and the    
OL,12,Fdebt will take decades to pay off.     
OL,14,FDavid Malpass told the BBC the same    
OL,15,Fpolicy was being adopted to help people
OL,16,Fcope with rising energy bills.         
OL,18,F"Governments are saying we will take   
OL,19,Fcare of everyone, which is just too    
OL,20,Fexpensive," he said.                   
